title: Osmonds Live Wembley Arena London 5-31-2008 (PPV)
description:
Here in MP4 format and ipod ready is the Osmonds 50th anniversary concert at Wembley Arena in London on May 31, 2008 (PPV).  This was an excellent concert and includes all seven Osmonds.  Much, Much better concert than the horribly edited DVD they released from Las Vegas.

Part One:

Crazy Horses
Back On The Road Again
Lazy River
The Proud One
Yo Yo
Let Me In
Marie&#039;s Melody
He Ain&#039;t Heavy, He&#039;s My Brother
Hold Her Tight
The Plan Melody



Part Two:

ENJOY!!
